Details

Posted: 02-Nov-23

Location: Savannah, Georgia

Type: Full Time

Salary: Negotiable

Occupation:

Veterinarian

Species:

Canine
Feline

Preferred Education:

DVM or equivalent

 Pet Care is a privately owned, small animal, general practice near Savannah, GA (about 40 min SW of downtown Savannah) Two doctor practice with digital xray, in house lab (Abaxis), UA Sediment Analyzer, Zoetis AI Fecal technology. Has LVT's on staff. Four techs/DVM. Twenty minute appts for well visits/30 min sick appts.  Partnership potential. Full time is four days per week. 8-5 or 9-6. No weekends and no ER call. 30 days PTO. Full benefits. Salary range mid six figures depending upon experience. If interested in more details please contact Rebecca at vetnet5@aol.com or through this posting
